 is a rare example of a S=1/2 nanomagnet\nshowing an enhancement in the nuclear spin-lattice relaxation rate 1/T1 at\nintermediate temperatures.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 10 Apr 2013 01:51:43 GMT"}],"update_date":"2014-10-15"}
