 such as the\nexpansion rate. An under-density of roughly this scale and amplitude would be\nsufficient to resolve the apparent tension between direct measurements of the\nHubble constant and those inferred by Planck.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 10 Apr 2013 09:22:19 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Sun, 28 Apr 2013 10:10:37 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Tue, 30 Apr 2013 01:19:19 GMT"},{"version":"v4","created":"Tue, 9 Jul 2013 08:20:18 GMT"},{"version":"v5","created":"Tue, 6 Aug 2013 06:52:53 GMT"}],"update_date":"2013-09-09"}
