,2,5 in dimension d=3, with the initial datum of Behr, Necas and Wu [M2AN,\n2001]. Computations of order N=5 yield a quantitative improvement of the\nresults previously obtained for this initial datum in [Nonlinear Anal. 2012],\nwhere a Galerkin approximate solution was employed in place of the Reynolds\nexpansion.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 10 Apr 2013 14:22:05 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Wed, 4 Sep 2013 09:06:47 GMT"}],"update_date":"2013-12-09"}
